58
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,520
Mr Yu.

59
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:23,830
Wanzhen.

60
00:04:24,030 --> 00:04:24,990
No, no, no...

61
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:25,750
Wendy.

62
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:26,510
Got a minute?

63
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,550
I'm always available for you.

64
00:04:28,550 --> 00:04:29,190
Have a seat.

65
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:40,630
About the acquisition of Xinmiao,

66
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:42,160
what are your thoughts?

67
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,190
Well,

68
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:45,600
I'm thinking of acquiring Xinmiao first,

69
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:46,750
