85
00:05:09,870 --> 00:05:11,870
it's definitely a win-win situation.

86
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,920
Our company is fine

87
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:15,070
and we won't lose, of course.

88
00:05:15,990 --> 00:05:16,720
But what about you?

89
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:17,600
I...

90
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:20,720
If you sign the bet-on agreement,

91
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,190
it will be a double-edged sword.

92
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,480
But if I

93
