104
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:46,950
Blue Ocean

105
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:48,280
is your brainchild.

106
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,360
It's all of your work

107
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,480
for the past decade.

108
00:05:50,990 --> 00:05:52,550
If this acquisition

109
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:55,160
means your loss of control

110
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,160
