115
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,840
I have reason to be concerned.

116
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:13,870
Wanzhen, actually,

117
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:14,920
I've thought

118
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:17,040
about this a lot already.

119
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,550
It's basically two choices:

120
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,920
either let Blue Ocean grow

121
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,840
or maintain my personal control

122
00:06:22,990 --> 00:06:24,550
over the company.

123
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,630
