124
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:28,040
I choose

125
00:06:28,950 --> 00:06:30,990
to let Blue Ocean grow.

126
00:06:31,870 --> 00:06:32,840
You know investment.

127
00:06:32,990 --> 00:06:34,070
I know the Internet.

128
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:35,990
Over the past decade,

129
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:37,600
Blue Ocean and I

130
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,120
have been facing

131
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:41,040
these kinds of challenges and choices.

132
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:41,630
This time,

133
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:42,950
I need your investment.

134
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:44,360
If I miss

135
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,600
such a great opportunity,

136
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:48,390
Blue Ocean could stagnate.

137
00:06:48,870 --> 00:06:49,800
Or even worse,

138
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,390
it could face collapse

139
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:52,990
with no way out.

140
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:55,430
