151
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:14,600
Wanzhen,

152
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,840
don't you think my current situation

153
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:17,430
is perfect

154
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,840
for signing this agreement?

155
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,280
