157
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:24,600
You and the kid are gone,

158
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,280
but we left enough education funds

159
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,680
for our kid.

160
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:28,720
If you were

161
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,990
still around,

162
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:32,630
I'd hesitate and hold back.

163
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:35,190
