170
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:54,990
Same here.

171
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,430
New ruler, new officials.

172
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,920
Employees like us,

173
00:07:59,310 --> 00:08:00,630
with high salaries,

174
00:08:00,630 --> 00:08:01,800
not very obedient,

175
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,990
and occasionally tripping up the boss,

176
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,750
certainly have to go.

177
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:07,800
But you may stay.

178
00:08:07,990 --> 00:08:08,800
Why?

179
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,630
You're the content director,

180
00:08:10,630 --> 00:08:12,040
the core of the company.

181
00:08:13,430 --> 00:08:15,040
Who else could take on Xinmiao

182
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:16,990
besides Blue Ocean?

183
00:08:17,190 --> 00:08:17,750
Well, Mr Yu

184
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:19,190
has been trying to poach you, hasn't he?

185
00:08:19,430 --> 00:08:20,800
Could be someone else.

186
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:21,720
Have a bet?

187
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,600
Better not.

188
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,950
If it's someone else,

189
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:28,160
I might still have a chance.

190
00:08:28,630 --> 00:08:29,550
But if it's Yu Hai,

191
00:08:30,990 --> 00:08:32,630
I'd really be out.

192
00:08:34,070 --> 00:08:34,870
Why?

193
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,360
We are friends after all.

194
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:39,680
Look at me right now.

195
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:41,560
I still need maternity leave.

196
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:42,870
I can't occupy this position

197
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:44,200
without contributing.

198
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,960
That would be awkward even with friends.

199
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,960
Anyway, they can't fire you,

200
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,270
you're pregnant.

201
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,790
That's your lifeline.

202
00:08:56,790 --> 00:08:57,960
Any plans?

203
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:00,750
I'm thinking of

204
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:02,120
taking a 20-year annual leave,

205
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,200
traveling the world,

206
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:05,790
and maybe meeting a prince charming.

207
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,510
It'd be prefect

208
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:09,630
if I meet someone like Li Lin.

209
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:13,240
Or you can just give me

210
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,360
a photo of Li Lin,

211
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,360
and I'll carry it with me.

212
00:09:15,390 --> 00:09:16,390
Think it'll work?

213
00:09:16,510 --> 00:09:16,870
Come on.

214
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,360
He's no mascot.

215
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:23,910
What about you?

216
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:25,600
Any plans?

217
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,480
What's the use of my plans right now?

218
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:30,510
I'll just focus

219
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,960
on giving birth first.

220
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,390
Then you should stay home for now.

221
00:09:37,870 --> 00:09:39,480
When I'm back in charge,

222
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,030
