227
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,120
Meng'an.

228
00:10:14,270 --> 00:10:14,790
Honey!

229
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,560
Hello, Meng'an.

230
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,870
Yiduo.

231
