235
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,870
Yes, it's been a while.

236
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:34,120
I've been wanting to visit you

237
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,510
but never had the chance.

238
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,670
I'm glad you're here today.

239
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,750
You look great,

240
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,150
